Tin Falls 1.5% on London Metal Exchange; Aluminum and Nickel Prices Drop

-- B y   D a n   W e e k s
-- 
2011-08-04T10:17:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-04/tin-falls-1-5-on-london-metal-exchange-aluminum-and-nickel-prices-drop.html
Tin for three-month delivery fell 1.5
percent to $25,900 a metric ton on the London Metal Exchange.
Nickel slid 1.1 percent to $23,550 a ton and aluminum lost 1.2
percent to $2,495 a ton.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Weeks at 
 dweeks1@bloomberg.net  